{"tid":1223636,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求長輩圖:  林鄭認丈夫兒子擁有英國藉  不認為需要放棄","createTime":"2019-06-14T18:05:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T20:09:26.000Z","uid":5195,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ca551dcd61eda4936f5653d78ede22cd5c35d83e","tid":1223636,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T18:05:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E3%80%90%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA%E3%80%91%E5%A4%AB%E6%93%81%E5%B1%85%E8%8B%B1%E6%AC%8A-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%BA%E9%9C%80%E6%94%BE%E6%A3%84-70020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E6%2593%2581%25E5%25B1%2585%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%25AC%258A-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25EF%25BC%259A%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25A6%25BA%25E9%259C%2580%25E6%2594%25BE%25E6%25A3%2584-70020&d=YB8lrFeyQ%2BkzHCEHpdql8P4FZ2Hvuo87ztF5QEQ%2B7nM%3D&h=e5dc3d37\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E3%80%90%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA%E3%80%91%E5%A4%AB%E6%93%81%E5%B1%85%E8%8B%B1%E6%AC%8A-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%BA%E9%9C%80%E6%94%BE%E6%A3%84-70020</a><br />\n<br />\n【專訪】林鄭月娥自辭職參選特首後，其一向低調的丈夫林兆波成為傳媒追訪對象，她指丈夫不打算「應付」記者，「佢只係做番真性情嘅人，唔係好似我咁選行政長官」，但她形容丈夫非常配合傳媒，更笑言丈夫應加入政府，有助搞好與傳媒關係。另外，林太承認丈夫早年透過居英權計劃擁有英國籍，但只視作旅遊證件，不認為需要放棄。採訪：馮振超、鄭秀韻 攝影：黃文山、鍾式明、林俊源<br />\n林太競選辦早前回覆傳媒查詢時表示，1990年英國政府推出居英權計劃，林太與家人透過此計劃獲得英國國籍；林太於2007年出任發展局長時已放棄英籍，將來應該不會重新申請，而丈夫林兆波及兩名兒子林節思與林約希至今仍擁有英籍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林太接受本報訪問時表示，「回歸前有居英權計劃，嗰個係所謂多一個旅遊證件嘅啫，佢有呢個旅遊證件」，但她說，「我唔覺得佢需要放棄」。"},{"pid":"30790b77ed4e0f1505b44256fbbe4c9100fb558e","tid":1223636,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T18:27:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ac9cf0bc32614ac4ea58bd752126a0b80a6b3d","tid":1223636,"uid":97223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T19:38:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1223676/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1223676/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"6f7338893e98d77f966ed425783fd3600b30e8d5","tid":1223636,"uid":137078,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T19:43:16.000Z","msg":"97年後出生冇bno我死都會同你老母攬炒呀死八婆閪"},{"pid":"f73ebb6d4ee1289719eabafca063f2085e0d3cbc","tid":1223636,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T20:08:25.000Z","msg":"長輩圖：柒婆搞亂香港然後退休後可以返英國安享晚年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e0eddad0e3f0e59e1f7d15b74dba860e3825f8e","tid":1223636,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T20:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df7aead6756cdb579d4494b6632124b78aa65dbe","tid":1223636,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T20:09:26.000Z","msg":"［文宣升級］長輩式反攻保皇FB Page<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cOfzjS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cOfzjS</a>"}]}